NAME
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Color - Determine color depth and whether
    to use color or not

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.002 of
    Role::TinyCommons::TermAttr::Color (from Perl distribution
    Role-TinyCommons-TermAttr-Color), released on 2020-06-06.

DESCRIPTION
    These use Term::App::Util::Color as backend.

PROVIDED METHODS
  termattr_use_color
  termattr_color_depth
